  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/io/Serializable.html
  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/invoke/SerializedLambda.html
  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/invoke/SerializedLambda.html#getImplClass--

